Assuming that I would be writing a code to use it, that means
nothing to me. Same applies to other fields of this struct.

You should likely be adding some formula explaining how to
calculate the threshold, either here, or inside a .rst file
(with would likely works better). If this is kept at a .rst file,
you'll likely need to add a note on this struct pointing to the
rst file (or a Sphinx ref).

> + * @__reserved0:	reserved
> + * @cg:	Gain coefficient for threshold calculation
> + * @ci:	Intensity coefficient for threshold calculation
> + * @__reserved1:	reserved
> + * @r_nf:	Number of frames
> + */
> +struct ipu3_uapi_bnr_static_config_thr_coeffs_config {
